==English==

===Phrase===
'''[[but]] [[who]]'s [[counting]]'''
#{{idiom}} Used as a [[retort]] or [[comeback]], often to [[deprecate]] oneself or another for excessive concern or attention to 
#:''There are only 258 more shopping days until Christmas, '''but who's counting'''?''
#:''You've made that mistake eight times now. '''But who's counting?'''''

